        <div class=\"tname\">邓  智</div>\n                                <div class=\"tposition\">长聘副教授 </div>\n                                <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"tcontent\">\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>博士、长聘副教授</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>电  话: 01062771961</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>邮  箱: dengz@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                   <p></p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                        </div>\n    </div>\n    <ul class=\"right-column-menu tright-column-menu\">  \n                     \n       <li class=\"on\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">教育背景</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">工作经历</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">教学工作</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">研究领域</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">研究概况</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">学术成果</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">学术兼职</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">奖励荣誉</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n    </ul> \n    \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-on\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2002.10月—2005.07<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>清华大学，获得工程物理专业博士学位</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2000.10月—2002.10<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>日本东京大学，获得量子工学与系统工程专业硕士学位</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>1995.09月—1999.07<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>清华大学，获得工程物理专业学士学位</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n</div></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2018.12-至今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系，长聘副教授</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2009.12-2018.11<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系，副教授</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">（2012年5月-9月，美国布鲁克海文国家实验室，访问学者）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2007.09-2009.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系，助理研究员</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>讲授《物理信号处理》、《核仪器原理》本科生课程；讲授《高等核电子学》研究生课程</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>指导硕士研究生毕业4名，博士研究生毕业1名，在读6名</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">从事核技术及应用方向的研究，主要包括辐射探测与成像的读出电子学技术，特别是专用集成芯片的设计研究。针对粒子和天文物理实验、医疗和工业成像和国土安全等应用，开展高密度、低噪声、高时间分辨数模混合集成芯片的研制，涉及粒子物理与成像原理、探测器信号产生机制以及电路原理和信号处理技术等多个交叉学科。</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2021.01至2025.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>融合动态能谱与个性化建模的冠状动脉容积成像方法与关键技术，国家自然科学基金项目，技术骨干；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2020.07至2022.07<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>国产超高速全数字化专用芯片关键技术研究与产业化，科技部重点研发计划项目，技术骨干</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2020.06至2024.05<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>NICA-MPD 新型电磁量能器关键技术合作研究，科技部重点研发计划项目，技术骨干</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2020.01至2023.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>大动态范围、高带宽低温高纯锗探测器CMOS前端ASIC关键技术研究，国家自然科学基金项目，负责</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2016.07至2021.06<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>高能环形正负电子对撞机相关的物理和关键技术预研究，科技部重点研发计划项目，技术骨干</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2015.01至2019.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>高压缩重子物质的物理实验研究，国家973计划项目，技术骨干</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2014.01至2017.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>低温辐射探测器CMOS集成前端电路设计研究，国家自然科学基金项目，负责</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2013.01至2016.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>基于光子计数探测器的X光能谱CT成像研究，国家自然科学基金项目，技术骨干</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2012.01至2014.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>新型CZT半导体X射线和γ射线探测器研制，科技部国家重大科学仪器设备开发专项，技术骨干</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2010.01至2012.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>一种高密度、高计数率、高时间分辨MRPC探测器读出ASIC的研制，国家自然科学基金项目，负责</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2010.01至2013.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>基于光电效应的空间X射线偏振仪研究，国家自然科学基金天文仪器专项，技术骨干</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2008.01至2011.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span>新型密集阵列探测器读出ASIC的研制，国家自然科学基金项目，技术骨干</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1. A Switched Capacitor Waveform Digitizing ASIC at Cryogenic Temperature for HPGe Detectors, IEEE Transactions on Nuclear Science, vol. 68, no.8, Liu Feng, Deng Zhi, Zhao Xinyuan, Liu Yinong, 2021</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2. Neural network-featured timing systems for radiation detectors: performance evaluation based on bound analysis, JINST, 16(09): P09019, Ai P, Deng Z, Wang Y, 2021</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">3. First experimental constraints on WIMP couplings in the effective field theory framework from CDEX, SCIENCE CHINA, 64(8), CDEX collaboration, 2021</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">4. Development of a pixel readout ASIC for CZT detectors for spectral X-ray photon-counting imaging applications, JOURNAL OF INSTRUMENTATION, 15(1), Wang X., Deng Z., Liu W., Liu Y., 2020</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">5. WASA: a low power front-end ASIC for time projection chambers in 65 nm CMOS, JOURNAL OF INSTRUMENTATION, 15(5), Liu W., Zhao X., Deng Z., Li F., Gu X., Li Y., Qi H., 2020</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">6. Cryogenic Bandgap Reference Circuit With Compact Model Parameter Extraction of MOSFETs and BJTs for HPGe Detectors, IEEE Transactions on Nuclear Science, vol. 67, no. 10, pp. 2209–2216, Liu, Feng, Zhi Deng, Yinong Liu, 2020,</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">7. Development of the full-chain cryogenic readout electronics for the point-contact HPGe detectors, NIMA, vol. 947, Liu Feng, Deng Zhi, He Li, Liu Yinong, 2019</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">8. Evaluation and lifetime study of a cryogenic SAR ADC for HPGe detectors in low-background physics experiments, JOURNAL OF INSTRUMENTATION, vol.14, Liu F., Xue T., Deng Z., Liu Y., 2019</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">9. GERO: a general SCA-based readout ASIC for micro-pattern gas detectors with configurable storage depth and on-chip digitizer, NUCLEAR SCIENCE AND TECHNIQUES, 30(9), Zhao Xin-Yuan, Liu Feng, Deng Zhi, Liu Yi-Nong, 2019</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">10. An ultra-low noise cryogenic CMOS charge sensitive preamplifier for large volume point-contact HPGe detectors, Journal of Instrumentation, 13(08): P08019, Deng Z, He L, Liu F, et al., 2018.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">11. DIET: a multi-channel SiPM readout ASIC for TOF-PET with individual energy and timing digitizer[J]. Journal of Instrumentation, 13(07): P07023., Chen Y, Deng Z, Liu Y. , 2018</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">12. A multi-purpose readout electronics for CdTe and CZT detectors for x-ray imaging applications, SPIE proceeding, 10393: 103930E., Yue X B, Deng Z, Xing Y X, et al., 2017</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>IEEE高级会员</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>核电子学与核探测技术分会辐射探测微电子学专委会，副主任委员</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">● </span>2017年获粒子物理前沿卓越创新中心“青年优秀人才”</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    \n    \n    \n</form>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--网页主体部分 end-->\n    <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n    <!--底部-- begin-->\n    <div class=\"links-box\">\n        <div class=\"links\">\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:20px;\"></div>\n            <div class=\"model-title\">\n                <div class=\"model\">常用链接</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"model-block\"></div>\n            <ul>\n      <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74493)\"><li>清华大学</li></a>\n    <a href=\"https://news.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74494)\"><li>清华新闻网</li></a>\n    <a href=\"https://tsinghua.cn.libguides.com/c.php?g=915369\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74495)\"><li>图书馆－核学科</li></a>\n</ul>\n            <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:41px;\"></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"copy-right-box\">\n        <div style=\"width:100%;height:26px;\"></div>\n        <ul>\n            <script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/mp4video.js\"></script>\n<li>地址：清华大学工程物理系（刘卿楼）</li> \n<li>邮编：100084</li> \n<li>电话：010-62785727</li> \n<li>邮箱：gwbgs@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn</li>\n        </ul>\n        <div style=\"width:100%;height:10px;\"></div>\n        <!-- 版权内容请在本组件\"内容配置-版权\"处填写 -->\n<div class=\"copy-right\">Copyright <span>©</span> 2020 清华大学工程物理系 All Right Reserved&nbsp;<script type=\"text/javascript\">var cnzz_protocol = ((\"https:\" == document.location.protocol) ? \"https://\" : \"http://\");document.write(unescape(\"%3Cspan id='cnzz_stat_icon_1277133078'%3E%3C/span%3E%3Cscript src='\" + cnzz_protocol + \"s5.cnzz.com/z_stat.php%3Fid%3D1277133078%26show%3Dpic' type='text/javascript'%3E%3C/script%3E\"));</script